reviewText:
This video is just a smattering of what this Artist has done to inspire the makeup world. To think that this man did all these characters to himself with less technically advanced products and more.
Even though there are parts that lack the detailing to allow one to copy the effects, freeze frame will overlook that short coming. Other than watching James Cagney portray Lon Chaney in The Man of a Thousand Faces some of the characters in this video will never be seen again.
All in all this was worth it.
